Angelina COLELLO and Joseph J. Colello, Plaintiffs-Appellants, v. Eric E. SUNDQUIST, DefendantAppellee. No. 231, Docket 23856. United States Court of Appeals Second Circuit. Argued Jan. 12, 1956. Decided Jan. 12, 1956. William Auerbach, New York City, for appellants. Evans, Orr, Walsh, Gourlay & Pacelli, New York City (William F. Laffan, Jr., Elmhurst, of counsel), for appellee.

Before CLARK, Chief Judge, and FRANK and LUMBARD, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed in open court on the opinion below, 137 F.Supp. 649,
